OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine,
OL,6,Fsunny evening for many, especially
OL,7,Finland, but cloudier and perhaps misty
OL,8,Ffor many coastal parts. Cloud
OL,9,Fspreading inland overnight, but
OL,10,Fremaining largely dry with a light
OL,11,Fnortheasterly breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FEarly cloud retreating to
OL,14,Fthe coast through the morning. Largely
OL,15,Fsunny skies follow, but perhaps hazier
OL,16,Fnear coasts. Warm in the sunshine,
OL,17,Fthough coastal parts cooler with an
OL,18,Fonshore breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
