OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FGenerally cloudy mornings with
OL,7,Fbrighter afternoons to follow.
OL,8,FRemaining largely dry throughout.
OL,9,FBreezy at times, especially along the
OL,10,Fcoast. Temperatures remaining above
OL,11,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
